## FAQ

**Do I need the full constitution?** No. Behavior module for daily use. Heartbeat for projects.

**How do I check if the AI is hallucinating?** Type `CTRL_VERIFY`.

**My prompts aren't getting good results.** Type `CTRL_PROMPT_CHECK` for analysis and recommendations.

**The AI keeps making the same error.** Circuit Breaker should trigger after 3 same-type errors. If it doesn't, tell the AI explicitly: "You've made this error 3 times. Switch to SOURCE_LOCKED and I'll provide the reference."

**Can the AI verify its own work?** With limitations. VerifyLens (S27.7) forces structural separation but cannot eliminate the fundamental bias. For critical outputs, cross-check with a second AI.

**Does this work on free AI tiers?** Yes. IAP auto-adapts. Grounding Gate works on all tiers.

**Can I modify the framework?** Yes. Follow Meta-Update Protocol. EVOLVE pass mandatory.
